{"word":"G1765 - ἐνισχύω - enischýō - en-is-khoo'-o - Strengthen","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνισχύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">enischýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-is-khoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Strengthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பலப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to grow strong, to receive strength"},{"paragraph":"2. to make strong, to strengthen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G2480 - ἰσχύω - ischýō - is-khoo'-o/2480\">G2480</a>; to <i>invigorate</i> (transitively or reflexively): - strengthen.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}